yet when the men of ulthar and nir and hatheg crushed their fears and scaled that haunted steep by day in search of barzai the wise , they found graven in the naked stone of the summit a curious and cyclopean symbol fifty cubits wide , as if the rock had been riven by some titanic chisel .
and the symbol was like to one that learned men have discerned in those frightful parts of the pnakotic manuscripts which were too ancient to be read .
this they found .
barzai the wise they never found , nor could the holy priest atal ever be persuaded to pray for his soul repose .
moreover , to this day the people of ulthar and nir and hatheg fear eclipses , and pray by night when pale vapors hide the and the moon .
